headline: Thanksgiving Sunday Sets New U.S. Air Travel Record. Why Airline Stocks Are Falling.

headline: United, Southwest turn to debit
summary: The airlines’ loyalty programs are responding to the millions of Americans who prefer to use a debit card for purchases in lieu of credit.
